snippet.title: The 46th - Free 'Shooting Range' Demo - Unreal Engine 4
snippet.description:
Download the demo now on our website and destroy those f@*&1¢g targets!
Challenge accepted ?!

▇  www.the46th-game.com

We hope you'll enjoy our demo and look forward to your feedback!

Please note that this demo is only intended to give a short overview of the firearm gameplay and the visual style of the game. The environments presented in the demo do not reflect the ones in
the final game.

If you are a great lord, support us on Tipeee:
